1
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:23,840
♪The world decays, in gloom I stray♪

2
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,900
♪Right and wrong, in frost engraved♪

3
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:32,750
♪On dreams of love, blades clash and sway♪

4
00:00:36,590 --> 00:00:39,240
♪Alone I ride, blood still unswayed♪

5
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:42,370
♪Through heaven's mirth and earth's despair♪

6
00:00:42,930 --> 00:00:48,370
♪Toasting the moon, I drink the chill air♪

7
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,800
♪Though hearts like battlefields may be♪

8
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:55,300
♪Let fate write its uncertainty♪

9
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:58,480
♪From this life to the great unknown♪

10
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:05,150
♪Who'll stand with me, on thrones unknown?♪

11
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:10,400
♪I'll wander through this life to guard you♪

12
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:13,660
♪Through mortal realms, serene I roam♪

13
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:17,520
♪With you, the world becomes my home♪

14
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:21,400
♪Unbroken, bold, as I have sworn♪

15
00:01:21,580 --> 00:01:25,970
♪I'll roam this life, and feel no torn♪

16
00:01:26,170 --> 00:01:29,320
♪Our souls embraced, no regret born♪

17
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:33,100
♪By twilight's lamp, though night be worn♪

18
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:36,750
♪Through deepest dark, I'll find the morn♪

19
00:01:36,750 --> 00:01:40,990
=Fight For Love=

20
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,940
=Episode 6=

21
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:25,720
♪Snow falls silent, soft and light♪

22
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:30,980
♪Tinting strands of hair in white♪

23
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:36,250
♪Through the sorrows of the past, I tread♪

24
00:02:37,050 --> 00:02:41,810
♪Till my heart finds rest at last♪

25
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:46,180
♪Blades may strike and words may sting♪

26
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:51,790
♪I'll stand fierce through everything♪

27
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:57,220
♪With you, I ask the earth and sky♪

28
00:02:58,010 --> 00:03:03,700
♪Our love, like ink, will never die♪

29
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:10,300
♪A moment, a lifetime♪

30
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:15,490
♪As long as I breathe, I'll stand by your side♪

31
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:20,880
♪Our vow is carved where walls arise♪

32
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:26,110
♪Time won't dim the fire in our eyes♪

33
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:28,960
The Wei family's century of merit

34
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,800
was bought with thousands,

35
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:34,000
tens of thousands of lives

36
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,840
from our clan.

37
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,150
It must not,

38
00:03:38,470 --> 00:03:41,150
and will not, fall here.

39
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:44,520
If His Majesty insists on condemning Wei Yun,

40
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:48,400
we will kneel here without rising.

41
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:52,030
Even if we freeze to death,

42
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,960
we will

43
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,750
hold him up.

44
00:03:57,820 --> 00:04:02,820
(Chengqing Gate)

45
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,640
(Brother Wei Jun,)

46
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,190
(you broke your promise.)

47
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,960
(But you died for our state.)

48
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,870
(You are a hero.)

49
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,080
(From here on,)

50
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,310
(Chengqing Gate)

51
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:25,800
(even if I am alone,)

52
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:28,430
(I'll uncover the truth.)

53
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,120
(I won't let the traitor who leaked)

54
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,870
(the crossbow plans go free.)

55
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,240
(May your spirit)

56
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:40,600
(rest.)

57
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:57,940
(Chengqing Gate)

58
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,400
Eat.

59
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,240
Lord Cao says

60
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,920
that you spent years on campaign

61
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,680
and is used to this food.

62
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,360
You'd

63
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,160
better eat.

64
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,360
No one

65
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,750
will visit you

66
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:23,800
again.

67
00:05:32,260 --> 00:05:37,980
(Chengqing Gate)

68
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,640
Han.

69
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,640
Wei Qiu,

70
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,560
escort Lady Han back.

71
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,470
Yu,

72
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,830
Lan is pregnant.

73
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:53,950
Let her return too.

74
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,430
Wei Qiu,

75
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,430
escort Lady Lan as well.

76
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,840
Careful.

77
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:20,180
(Tablet of Wei Zhong, Marquis of Zhenguo)

78
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:25,820
(Chengqing Gate)

79
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,240
Look, entire Wei family

80
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,090
are still kneeling.

81
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:39,240
They've been kneeling a long time.

82
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,080
Yes.

83
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:41,070
And right here at the gate.

84
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:45,700
(Zhang An, Deputy Minister of Personnel)

85
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:48,590
Deputy Minister Zhang,

86
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:50,960
where are you going?

87
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,000
Mr. cao,

88
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,430
I'm going to another gate.

89
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:55,830
I won't enter from here.

90
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,270
Why?

91
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,880
Heroes rest here.

92
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,430
How could I take their path?

93
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,240
The side gate is enough.

94
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,360
Such pretense.

95
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:23,710
Lady Chu,

96
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,630
why pretending like this?

97
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,190
If kneeling could move His Majesty,

98
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,720
what use

99
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:30,710
is our law?

100
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,680
Mr. Cao is right.

101
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:36,720
You ignore the law and try

102
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,000
to coerce the throne.

103
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,240
The law may be rigid.

104
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:48,360
Our laws exist for the people.

105
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:51,270
Duke of Ning and Lord Cao,

106
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,790
you've reversed cause and effect.

107
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:53,990
Teacher.

108
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,200
Sincerity

109
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,270
can pierce stone.

110
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,840
Academician Gu,

111
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:20,670
what does that old man's

112
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,080
saying mean?

113
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:24,750
Mr. Cao,

114
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,080
the snow is coming.

115
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,150
Best hurry.

116
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,510
If you can't take it,

117
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,440
go rest a while.

118
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:58,350
I'm fine.

119
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,200
If you can stand,

120
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,240
so can I.

121
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,800
Sister,

122
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:12,510
are you alright?

123
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,390
Just because you called me "Sister,"

124
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,000
I must hold on.

125
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,840
Since we're here,

126
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,630
there's no turning back.

127
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,320
Linyang, it's freezing.

128
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,270
Don't go.

129
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,320
Chu Linyang!

130
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:41,710
Chu Linyang!

131
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,150
Dressed like this,

132
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:56,320
are you going to the palace?

133
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:04,670
You returned from Fengling injured

134
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:07,750
and haven't attended court.

135
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,870
Now, with the Wei family in crisis,

136
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:11,270
you go despite illness?

137
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:13,440
Chu Yu is already married into the Wei family.

138
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,480
At this moment

139
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,840
you should avoid suspicion.

140
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,870
Otherwise His Majesty

141
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:21,030
will doubt our families' ties.

142
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,320
If we

143
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,510
anger Duke of Ning,

144
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,790
how will the Chu family survive?

145
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,200
Mother,

146
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,600
in the wind and snow at the Chu Mansion,

147
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,360
someone can holds an umbrella for us.

148
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:46,200
But before the palace gates,

149
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:48,630
no one shields Yu from the storm.

150
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,630
I'm going today

151
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,110
not for anyone else,

152
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,030
but for her.

153
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,360
She chose to marry into the Wei family.

154
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,390
She chose to kneel at the palace gates.

155
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,390
Every bit of suffering

156
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:02,030
is her own doing.

157
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,800
Linyang,

158
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:04,960
this family

159
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,910
isn't only her.

160
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,840
If something happens to you,

161
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,360
what will Mother and I do?

162
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,440
Do you only

163
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,240
see Chu Yu as you sister,

164
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,120
but not me?

165
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,320
Jin,

166
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:19,360
if you were the one kneeling at the gate today,

167
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,840
I would go without hesitation

168
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,720
to shield you as well.

169
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:24,710
I don't believe you.

170
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:27,150
Linyang, make your choice

171
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,720
between Jin and Yu today.

172
00:12:31,030 --> 00:12:32,630
If you step out that gate,

173
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:35,080
you lose me as your sister.

174
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:36,590
Jin,

175
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,510
stop being childish.

176
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,510
I must go today.

177
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:44,710
Mother,

178
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:47,080
Yu is holding up

179
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,030
the entire Wei family alone.

180
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,750
No one stands behind her.

181
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:52,840
I am her brother,

182
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,440
her family.

183
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,480
How can I do nothing?

184
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,360
Brother!

185
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:27,920
Your Majesty,

186
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,080
Wei Yun is now

187
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,720
imprisoned by the Court

188
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,560
of Judicial Review,

189
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:34,030
yet Minister Cao

190
00:13:34,390 --> 00:13:36,200
has found no solid evidence

191
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,600
against the Wei family.

192
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,270
Without evidence,

193
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,720
Wei Yun should be released.

194
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:44,150
I beg Your Majesty to show mercy.

195
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:45,750
I, Chu Linyang, implore

196
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,120
Your Majesty to pardon Wei Yun.

197
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,270
Young General Chu,

198
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,720
you came to court too today.

199
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:53,720
My father died for the state.

200
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,160
Now

201
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,600
I am weak in body, and

202
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,750
my younger sister bears the burden alone,

203
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,720
defending Wei family's honor

204
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:02,630
with all her loyalty.

205
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:04,720
I cannot bear it,

206
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,480
so I beg for her sake.

207
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:14,480
General Chu, are you trying to sway

208
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,240
His Majesty with sentiment?

209
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:31,380
Seventy thousand loyal souls

210
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,240
lie buried in Baidi Valley, Your Majesty.

211
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,750
This cannot be investigated

212
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:35,870
overnight.

213
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:37,910
Please give

214
00:14:37,910 --> 00:14:39,200
the Court more time.

215
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,840
I will definitely

216
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,080
unveil the truth.

217
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,030
If the Wei family is truly innocent,

218
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,440
we will clear their name.

219
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,230
Your Majesty,

220
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,510
seventy thousand

221
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:57,120
died because Wei Zhong

222
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,390
sought merit and acted rashly.

223
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,480
Seven members of the Wei family died.

224
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,160
Are their lives considered lives,

225
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:03,670
but the seventy thousand

226
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:05,030
are not?

227
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:10,200
Duke of Ning,

228
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:17,480
hearing you speak

229
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:18,600
so confidently,

230
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,510
one might think

231
00:15:20,790 --> 00:15:21,750
you actually

232
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,320
was there in Baidi Valley.

233
00:15:24,390 --> 00:15:25,600
Your Highness, you jest.

234
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,320
I am but a civil official,

235
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:29,000
unfit for the battlefield.

236
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,270
Good.

237
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,240
Since you insist,

238
00:15:41,510 --> 00:15:42,750
I will support you.

239
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,150
A war I choose to fight,

240
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:52,510
I never lose.

241
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,040
Changming?

242
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,600
You came too?

243
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:08,240
Forgive me, Brother.

244
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,550
I shouldn't be here,

245
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,910
but this concerns Huan.

246
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:14,840
As his aunt,

247
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,680
I cannot stay away.

248
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,360
Her Highness is right.

249
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,750
Since the Crown Prince

250
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:24,150
and General Yao are here,

251
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,120
let them recount

252
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,550
the events so His Majesty

253
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:29,360
may judge fairly.

254
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,000
Huan is grown,

255
00:16:34,510 --> 00:16:35,870
brave and capable

256
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:36,960
even in the battlefield.

257
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,510
About what happened in Baidi Valley,

258
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,480
even if he says nothing,

259
00:16:42,030 --> 00:16:42,910
I believe

260
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:44,510
the Court

261
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:47,030
will uncover the truth.

262
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:50,360
As crown prince

263
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,600
and His Majesty's only bloodline,

264
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,840
he knows Him best.

265
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,270
His Majesty never spares

266
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,960
a guilty man

267
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:02,150
nor wrongs an innocent one.

268
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,280
Am I right,

269
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:05,800
Huan?

270
00:17:18,270 --> 00:17:19,150
Father,

271
00:17:19,150 --> 00:17:20,510
though seventy thousand died,

272
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,400
the Wei family

273
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,310
has always been loyal.

274
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,560
Everything they did

275
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,920
was for the realm

276
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:27,760
and the people.

277
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,220
Their merits outweigh faults.

278
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:31,400
Please spare Wei Yun.

279
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,280
Your Majesty,

280
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:39,880
if a man sheds blood

281
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:41,350
for the realm,

282
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:43,400
yet his widows and orphans

283
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:45,480
must still suffer cold and scorn,

284
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,960
if a family that has fought

285
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:48,800
for four generations

286
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:51,160
still leaves its descendants disgraced,

287
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,350
then the hearts

288
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:54,750
of those

289
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,480
seventy thousand

290
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:58,240
who died will freeze.

291
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,080
Your Majesty,

292
00:18:10,830 --> 00:18:12,790
for the Wei family's

293
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:14,510
century of loyalty,

294
