00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:02,880
The Wei family hasn't fallen.

605
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,000
And I believe

606
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:09,280
winter's snow will melt,

607
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,480
