629
00:41:32,840 --> 00:41:33,840
Please don't get angry.

630
00:41:34,550 --> 00:41:36,280
Drink some tea please.

631
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:41,910
Chusheng

632
00:41:42,150 --> 00:41:43,670
