643
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,070
Thank you for the tea.

644
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:42,350
Wait.

645
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:43,640
Let me

646
00:42:44,510 --> 00:42:45,840
