647
00:43:23,280 --> 00:43:24,150
You know it's hot now?

648
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:26,440
So listen.

649
00:43:27,360 --> 00:43:29,320
Otherwise, go back to the southwest.

650
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:31,800
There's only cold tea there.

651
00:43:43,400 --> 00:43:44,800
I will remember

652
00:43:45,510 --> 00:43:46,510
your teachings,

653
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:49,280
Duke.

654
00:43:53,150 --> 00:43:53,990
Chusheng!

